verbose_text: KEGG analyses on those higher expression genes, which are induced by Lactobacillus, identified several critical signaling pathways, including Janus activated kinase (JAK)-STAT signaling pathway, Toll like receptor signaling pathway, NF-kappaB signaling pathway, TNF signaling pathway, intestinal immune network for IgA production, and cytokine-cytokine receptor interaction.
evidence: activated kinase (JAK)-STAT signaling pathway, Toll-like receptor
